{"_id":"0xdxcUQkKDS0XbF2","name":"GM Macros","content":"<h1>Macros for SWADE</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/sundries/gaming/playing-cards-grey.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Adventure Card - Table or Deck</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>You have to macros! <strong>Adventure Deck - Deck</strong> and <strong>Adventure Deck - Table</strong>. The Table one uses a table and the deck one uses a deck. Choose the macro you want to import to the world.</li>\n<li>Select one or more tokens.</li>\n<li>The Everyone option you give cards to all selected tokens. You can pick just one player.</li>\n<li>You need to choose the table with your adventure cards.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Notes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The player will receive a item (under gear) for each card. He can click on it to send to chat or open to see.</li>\n<li>If you create an additional stat called adventurecards the players can set the amount of cards they will receive.</li>\n<li>If didn't create the additional stat, the macro will read the rank. Novice = 1, etc.</li>\n<li>If you create an additional stat and did not have a rank that the macro can understand, the player will receive 1 card.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>About the Table</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The item created for the players will have the image in the table entry as the card and the text in the table as the item name.</li>\n<li>If you use the reset button this will reset the table and remove all cards from the tokens.</li>\n<li>You can set the default table in settings.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Create an Additional Stat</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.guide-macros-for-swade.PpSCLfufdR6THMeA]{Create an Additional Stat}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/sundries/gaming/playing-cards.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Chase</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to Macros for SWADE Settings and set the name of your deck. It should match your world deck name.</li>\n<li>Open a test scene (get it from the compendium: <strong>Scenes - Macros for SWADE</strong>).</li>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Customization</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">You can create your own scene. </span>You can place the card whatever you want.</p>\n<p>You will notice in the test scene transparent tiles. You can move them to any place. You can copy and paste them into a new scene.</p>\n<p>You can change their dimensions to match your cards art. But, the size matches official scale modules, so it's advised to press Alt to change the transparent tile size and shift to move it.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Notes</strong></p>\n<p>The transparent tile path: modules/swademacros/images/card_transparent.webp</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/weapons/thrown/dynamite-simple-brown.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Deviation</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro and the chat will tell will where to land the template. Then, just lick on the scene.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/deviation.webp\" width=\"286\" height=\"200\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>You need to install:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/trioderegion/warpgate/releases/latest/download/module.json\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Warp Gate</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/commodities/tech/detonator-timer.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Dramatic Tasks</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro and choose how many players and the desired difficult.</li>\n<li>It'll whisper to you a suggestion.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-underline-header)\"><img style=\"border:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\" src=\"icons/skills/wounds/bone-broken-marrow-red.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Falling Damage Calculator</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select/target tokens. Run the macro.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/sundries/books/book-backed-blue-gold.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Interludes</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select some tokens. They must have be linked and have an user.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The macro will whisper for each token owner the interlude outcome.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/environment/people/charge.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Mass Battle</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>Fill the data.</li>\n<li>After the roll you can click in the chat button to sabe the roll to a journal.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/massbattle.webp\" width=\"280\" height=\"318\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-underline-header)\"><img style=\"border:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\" src=\"icons/sundries/gaming/dice-pair-white-green.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Mass Roll</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select some tokens and run the macro.</li>\n<li>You can roll the tokens traits or create a custom roll.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-underline-header)\"><img style=\"border:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\" src=\"icons/magic/time/clock-stopwatch-white-blue.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Quick Combat</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>It'll select ALL tokens in the active scene, send them to combat tracker.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>You can now mount the groups. Then press Begin Combat.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-underline-header)\"><img style=\"border:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\" src=\"icons/skills/social/trading-justice-scale-yellow.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Social Conflict</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>It'll open a dialog which will trigger the Challenge Tracker interface.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>This macro requires the module <a href=\"https://github.com/Larkinabout/fvtt-challenge-tracker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Challenge Tracker</a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-underline-header)\"><img style=\"border:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\" src=\"icons/skills/social/diplomacy-handshake.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Token Disposition Changer</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select/target some tokens.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>","img":"icons/sundries/gaming/playing-cards.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"tckKxzbezKvre3KI":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"26R0M4mnq6TPjaRs","name":"Alchemy","content":"<h1>Alchemy</h1>\n<p>You can search some items in the <strong>Items - Macros for SWADE</strong> compendium that will have a macro link in the description. </p>\n<p>Add the item to the actor. The actor can trigger a macro by oppening the item description and clicking on it while the token is selected.</p>\n<p>You don't need to import the macros.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>List</h2>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.O9B8XHw55mFC5HvP]{Potion of Healing}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.HyJrKnLUDQlzFZZx]{Potion of Strong Healing}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.qkbv0V8XCWmsi8jf]{Potion of Full Healing}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.QaRdwIgyB1DGRLTV]{Potion of Invigoration}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.ML9Gy67qo7ezqJRy]{Potion of Strong Invigoration}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.MwQKt4DnFgukATjp]{Potion of Strength}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.tYT28XjgiO1Sfzrn]{Potion of Giant Strength}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.PPUokcYS7TDOUigr]{Potion of Speed}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.qL2RtbAqCor5hsCu]{Potion of Flight}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.OTs3oACiGwVhAkhf]{Potion of Stoneskin}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swademacros.items-for-macros.DrKnBlj7NOkFoR2A]{Potion of Growth}</p>","img":"icons/sundries/gaming/playing-cards.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"dJvi2seC8CqTkxhs":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.CO16N35lwnALPCc3"}}}
